,"icon":124},"F.A.Q.","i-lucide-message-circle-question-mark",{"id":126,"title":13,"body":127,"description":211,"extension":212,"links":213,"meta":214,"navigation":215,"path":14,"seo":216,"stem":15,"__hash__":217},"docs\u002F1.getting-started\u002F2.contributing.md",{"type":128,"value":129,"toc":204},"minimark",[130,135,142,145,148,151,164,167,177,181,190,193],[131,132,134],"h2",{"id":133},"call-for-help","📣 Call for Help",[136,137,138,141],"p",{},[139,140,113],"a",{"href":114}," — the original creator of this site — is full of hiking stoke but not quite full of all the knowledge in the Rockies 🏔️.",[136,143,144],{},"This site isn't meant to be a one-hiker show… it's an open trailhead for a shared effort to make info better, richer, and more helpful for everyone 📚.",[136,146,147],{},"👋 Wanna Lend a Boot?",[136,149,150],{},"You're more than welcome to contribute if any of this sounds like you:",[152,153,154,158,161],"ul",{},[155,156,157],"li",{},"🌐 You know of great hiking groups we should highlight, or can help flesh out info on the ones already listed 📝",[155,159,160],{},"🥾 You're a hike organizer and want to share your vibe, style, and what folks should expect on your adventures 💬",[155,162,163],{},"🔧 You've got trail wisdom to drop — whether it's safety tips, gear recs, or “I learned this the hard way” kind of knowledge 🧠",[136,165,166],{},"Whether it's a quick fix, a full section, or just a friendly pointer to better info — every little bit helps 🫶🌲\nLet's build this trail guide together! 🛠️🗺️✨",[136,168,169,170,176],{},"Use the 'Edit this page' link located to the right of each page to propose changes through ",[139,171,175],{"href":172,"rel":173},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fsamidalouche\u002Falberta-hiking-resources",[174],"nofollow","GitHub",".",[131,178,180],{"id":179},"license","📜 License",[136,182,183,184,189],{},"All this trail-loving info is shared under the ",[139,185,188],{"href":186,"rel":187},"https:\u002F\u002Fcreativecommons.org\u002Flicenses\u002Fby-sa\u002F4.0\u002F",[174],"Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License"," 🌍",[136,191,192],{},"That means:",[152,194,195,198,201],{},[155,196,197],{},"✅ You can use it",[155,199,200],{},"🛠️ You can remix it",[155,202,203],{},"🔁 You can share it — as long as you give credit and share it under the same terms 🎉♻️",{"title":205,"searchDepth":206,"depth":207,"links":208},"",1,2,[209,210],{"id":133,"depth":207,"text":134},{"id":179,"depth":207,"text":180},"Contribute to this site","md",null,{},{"icon":16},{"title":13,"description":211},"y94E3oGvhd15e8caeacqWmSjC5Ee3F1osi5qhCGVQh4",[219,221],{"title":10,"path":6,"stem":7,"description":220,"icon":11,"children":-1},"Welcome to Alberta Hiking Resources.",{"title":10,"path":20,"stem":21,"description":222,"icon":24,"children":-1},"A few solid options to find your hiking fam.",1773623245159]